{"tid":1303233,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 如何令TVB變下一個亞視？","createTime":"2019-07-10T08:43:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T08:43:04.000Z","uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"990c0c2044d8472dc56536f60ea9c5fef09624a2","tid":1303233,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:43:04.000Z","msg":"點樣可以系統化TVB杯葛行動？<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益，<br />\n<br />\n只有系統化先可以集合力量令TVB驚，<br />\n<br />\n正如遊行要正規地做左出黎，先會召集到200萬人，<br />\n<br />\n尋晚有個好例子，用梁振英恥與為伍個招，每日post:<br />\n<br />\n全力支持TVB廣告商<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1300810\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1300810</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n其實就好似杯葛撐送中餐廳咁，<br />\n<br />\n到頭來都無完全系統化到令人可以杯葛，<br />\n<br />\n最易用我已經覺得係呢個，插入左google map:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1Jxy3dCPOA5VYlsX8Jcw48GryWxkwn9tj&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.31653180798728%2C114.15173855547414&amp;z=14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D1Jxy3dCPOA5VYlsX8Jcw48GryWxkwn9tj%26shorturl%3D1%26ll%3D22.31653180798728%252C114.15173855547414%26z%3D14&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC9mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=0b3d8a05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1Jxy3dCPOA5VYlsX8Jcw48GryWxkwn9tj&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.31653180798728%2C114.15173855547414&amp;z=14</a><br />\n<br />\n個邊可否出個app 或網頁，非常user friendly地令人揀到合適餐廳？<br />\n<br />\n大家天方夜譚下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n----------------<br />\n另外想成立個杯葛TVB TG group，<br />\n<br />\n比鍵盤戰士一齊做野，<br />\n<br />\n最主要就係系統化比有心人知要杯葛邊啲品牌，<br />\n<br />\n例如幫手每日做恥與為伍post，<br />\n<br />\n真係會出力嘅留低TG.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}